Nick Clegg Wants to “Wring the Neck” of Bankers, FT Reports

-- B y   J a c k   J o r d a n
-- 
2011-03-12T09:56:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-12/nick-clegg-wants-to-wring-the-neck-of-bankers-ft-reports.html
U.K. Deputy Prime Minister  Nick Clegg  has raised the level of anti-banker rhetoric among the
country’s politicians, the FT reported, citing an interview on
BBC Radio Sheffield.  “I am like anyone else: you want to wring the neck of
these wretched people who behaved so irresponsibly and then we
are now having to bail them out,” Clegg said in the interview,
the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jack Jordan in  London  at 
 jjordan22@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 